{"tid":1329154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【 大 伏 】立 法 會 可 以 過 附 屬 法","createTime":"2019-07-18T06:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T06:31:04.000Z","uid":176112,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c923f647f37a70f7ec0693e879204dd3f49249d8","tid":1329154,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ksVhxRQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FksVhxRQ.png&h=f51fcf1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;附屬法例&quot;指<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">根據或憑藉任何條例</span></span>訂立並具有立法效力的文告、規則、規例、 命令、決議、公告、法院規則、附例或其他文書。附屬法例通常是由政府制定 的詳細規則及規例，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為實施某條例而須訂立的技術或程序上的細節。</span></span>"},{"pid":"9b43587db67a26dbcbf8ec3d957bb299ca8f5f4a","tid":1329154,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f060c3acb95a3780a82fa7110d85205396e7efc","tid":1329154,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8c09a3dff322261d18b4d1561c25e139fe5208","tid":1329154,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3c1a6e39472499f9884e27cccb323f95a184bd","tid":1329154,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde803e6b2ac0b7e4defe54dcebd94042a7c531d","tid":1329154,"uid":125349,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:30:26.000Z","msg":"1. 會都開唔到而家<br />\n2. 都係要立法會審議<br />\n<br />\n同普通修例一樣 冇分別 亦都冇特別"},{"pid":"b5d99c263111ec1f9b44d